    %p
      Submit issues to the
      %a{:href => 'https://github.com/marcpeabody/bjcp/issues', :target => '_blank'}Github project.
    %h3 Cheers
    %p
      Marc Peabody - Certified BJCP
      %br
      %a{:href => 'http://sodz.org', :target => '_blank'}SODZ Homebrew Club of Columbus, OH
      %br
      Twitter:
      %a{:href => 'http://twitter.com/marcpeabody', :target => '_blank'}@marcpeabody
